Enhance UI to match Instagram and Twitter
Enhance the UI and functionality of the feed, status bar, and main content layout to match Instagram and Twitter.
* **Feed Component (`app/components/feed.tsx`)** - Add advanced features like media previews, file size limits, and a polished design. - Enhance UI/UX to match Instagram and Twitter, including improved post interactions and a modern layout. - Add features like likes, comments, and shares. - Implement sorting and filtering options for posts. - Add a default post for display when no posts are available. - Integrate `ScrollArea` and `AnimatePresence` for smooth scrolling and animations.
* **Status Bar (`app/components/status-bar.tsx`)** - Update design to include user stories similar to Instagram. - Add functionality to create and share new stories. - Integrate `Dialog` for story creation with validation and toast notifications.
* **Main Content Layout (`app/page.tsx`)** - Redesign main content layout to resemble Instagram and Twitter home page. - Integrate `StatusBar`, `CreatePost`, and `Feed` components for a cohesive user experience.
